做网贷。。。", "content_rendered": "突然发现拼多多居然没有做网贷。。。", "last_modified": 1782003933, "replies": 41, "id": 1221710}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/eaae/339c/653_large.png?m=1678403810", "name": "vps", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/eaae/339c/653_normal.png?m=1678403810", "title": "VPS", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/vps", "topics": 8176, "footer": "", "header": "关于 VPS 购买和使用的讨论。", "title_alternative": "VPS", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/eaae/339c/653_mini.png?m=1678403810", "stars": 3965, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 653, "parent_node_name": "cloud"}, "member": {"id": 441006, "username": "SwEpoch", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/SwEpoch", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/addabd26c85b73e37b75405e0ef270bf?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/addabd26c85b73e37b75405e0ef270bf?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/addabd26c85b73e37b75405e0ef270bf?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1568278727, "last_modified": 1781952361, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "digwow", "last_touched": 1781985021, "title": "[陈恳求助] 现在能买的 VPS 线路有哪些", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1221665", "created": 1781953138, "deleted": 0, "content": "这几年一直都在使用机场，最近太不稳定了，动不动就拉闸，还要自己捣鼓各种分流，心累的很，所以有想法自建，独立节点自用自蹬。\r\n\r\n在论坛和各个频道研究了几天，定位：江苏电信，测下来感觉必须上 CN2GIA 线路才行，流量平时用量不多，大概 500G 左右。\r\n\r\n奈何搬瓦工现在有点贵，💲49/季度，也没有什么优惠码，有一点点舍不得，预算在 600 左右/年。\r\n\r\n刚刚接触自建，陈恳求助各位佬，有没有什么推荐的线路吗？ 想稳定用下去的。\r\n\r\n如果各位佬有想放生的线路，也可以加价收一下，论坛小透明在此感谢各位大佬。", "content_rendered": "<p>这几年一直都在使用机场，最近太不稳定了，动不动就拉闸，还要自己捣鼓各种分流，心累的很，所以有想法自建，独立节点自用自蹬。</p>\n<p>在论坛和各个频道研究了几天，定位：江苏电信，测下来感觉必须上 CN2GIA 线路才行，流量平时用量不多，大概 500G 左右。</p>\n<p>奈何搬瓦工现在有点贵，💲49/季度，也没有什么优惠码，有一点点舍不得，预算在 600 左右/年。</p>\n<p>刚刚接触自建，陈恳求助各位佬，有没有什么推荐的线路吗？ 想稳定用下去的。</p>\n<p>如果各位佬有想放生的线路，也可以加价收一下，论坛小透明在此感谢各位大佬。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1781953138, "replies": 32, "id": 1221665}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1777132346", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1777132346", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 239298, "footer": "", "header": "<!--\r\n一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。\r\n-->", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1777132346", "stars": 4496, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 693918, "username": "apollo007", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/apollo007", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ed76/9435/693918_mini.png?m=1728288909", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ed76/9435/693918_normal.png?m=1728288909", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ed76/9435/693918_large.png?m=1728288909", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ed76/9435/693918_xlarge.png?m=1728288909", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ed76/9435/693918_xxlarge.png?m=1728288909", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ed76/9435/693918_xxxlarge.png?m=1728288909", "created": 1717387944, "last_modified": 1728288909, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "FrankAdler", "last_touched": 1781874020, "title": "周末好无聊啊！有点为退休后无事可做发愁了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1221719", "created": 1782011088, "deleted": 0, "content": "大家周末都做点啥呀？孩子老婆带着，我在家里玩电脑，玩电脑也玩的无聊了，也不知道做点啥。将来计划再过几年退休，可是退休后做啥呢？感觉更加无聊了。", "content_rendered": "<p>大家周末都做点啥呀？孩子老婆带着，我在家里玩电脑，玩电脑也玩的无聊了，也不知道做点啥。将来计划再过几年退休，可是退休后做啥呢？感觉更加无聊了。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1782011088, "replies": 32, "id": 1221719}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_large.png?m=1644885960", "name": "car", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_normal.png?